name: Addison Taylor
text:
This park requires a Helmet and for each skater to fill out a liability waver, so you must be 18+ or accompanied by an adult. The gentleman on duty was very nice to me, improving my overall experience. The skate park is mostly street oriented; stairs, ledges, flatbars, C ledge, Manny pad drop off, hubbas and handrails. The "bowl" is more so a pool complete with pool coping, and is DIFFICULT to skate!!! Not your casual bowl session. In conclusion, if you want some perfect handrails and hubba down small, medium and large stairs then this your Park! Also lots of spectating area and a skatepark lobby with bathrooms a couch and TV to hang out and realx.
